  "title": "Flavorful Ukrainian English Muffin Hash",
  "description": "A tangy and bouncy one-pot Ukrainian dish featuring English muffins, cooked on a salt block with a nimono-simmer method, suitable for a Buddhist temple meal. This dish is a unique fusion of Ukrainian and English flavors.",
