  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the salt block over medium heat for 10 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped onions and cook until they are translucent.",
    "Add the chopped bell peppers and cook until they are tender.",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms and cook until they are soft.",
    "Add the cubed English muffins and stir to combine.",
    "Add the tomato paste and stir to combine.",
    "Add the vegetable broth and bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook for 10 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
